# NeurIPS 2026 Main Track Format Checklist

Source captured from the NeurIPS 2026 Main Track Handbook page:
https://neurips.cc/Conferences/2026/MainTrackHandbook

Local source of truth for this repo:
- LaTeX style: `Submission/neurips_2026.sty`
- Main paper source: `Submission/paper.tex`
- Build command: `.\tectonic.exe --keep-logs --keep-intermediates -p -o Submission\build Submission\paper.tex`

Submission PDF requirements:
- Submit one single PDF file.
- Use the official NeurIPS 2026 LaTeX style file.
- Do not use altered margins, altered font sizes, `fullpage`, or custom geometry overrides.
- Maximum PDF file size: 50 MB.
- Main content limit: 9 pages for initial submission, including figures and tables.
- References, optional appendices, and the mandatory paper checklist do not count toward the 9-page main content limit.
- Suggested PDF order: main paper content, references, appendices, NeurIPS paper checklist.

Anonymous submission requirements:
- Initial submission must be anonymized for double-blind review.
- Do not use the `final`, `preprint`, or `nonanonymous` style options for anonymous submission.
- Do not include acknowledgments at submission time.
- Avoid author-identifying text, links, supplementary paths, or repository references unless anonymized.

Camera-ready notes:
- Accepted camera-ready papers may use an additional content page.
- Camera-ready must include references, appendices, and checklist in the same PDF.
- Camera-ready papers must include funding and competing-interest disclosures.

Local automated checks:
- Build:
  `.\tectonic.exe --keep-logs --keep-intermediates -p -o Submission\build Submission\paper.tex`
- Log scan:
  `Select-String -Path Submission\build\paper.log -Pattern "error|undefined|Citation|Reference|Overfull|Underfull|Warning|Emergency stop|Fatal" -CaseSensitive:$false`
- Size:
  `Get-Item Submission\build\paper.pdf | Select-Object FullName,Length`
- Source compliance:
  `Select-String -Path Submission\paper.tex -Pattern "\\usepackage\[(final|preprint|nonanonymous)|\\begin\{ack\}|Acknowledgments|\\usepackage\{geometry\}|\\fontsize|\\addtolength|\\setlength\{\\textwidth|\\setlength\{\\textheight"`
- Structure:
  `Select-String -Path Submission\paper.tex -Pattern "^\\section|^\\appendix|^\\begin\{thebibliography\}|^\\section\*\{NeurIPS Paper Checklist\}"`

Main-content page marker check:
1. Insert this line immediately before `\begin{thebibliography}{99}` in a temporary copy:
   `\typeout{RCLS_MAIN_CONTENT_PAGE=\thepage}`
2. Build the temporary copy with Tectonic.
3. Confirm `RCLS_MAIN_CONTENT_PAGE <= 9`.
4. Delete the temporary copy after checking.

